001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo.bitcore;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
004import org.bitcoinj.base.Sha256Hash;
005
006import java.util.List;
007
008/**
009 * Result from Bitcore/Omni {@code getaddressutxos}.
010 */
011public class AddressUtxoResult {
012    private final Sha256Hash hash;
013    private final int height;
014    private final List<AddressUtxoInfo> utxos;
015
016    public AddressUtxoResult(@JsonProperty("hash")    Sha256Hash hash,
017                             @JsonProperty("height")  int height,
018                             @JsonProperty("utxos")   List<AddressUtxoInfo> utxos) {
019        this.hash = hash;
020        this.height = height;
021        this.utxos = utxos;
022    }
023
024    public Sha256Hash getHash() {
025        return hash;
026    }
027
028    public int getHeight() {
029        return height;
030    }
031
032    public List<AddressUtxoInfo> getUtxos() {
033        return utxos;
034    }
035}
